FBIS4-8607 "dreeu073_i_94015" FBIS-EEU-94-073 Daily Report 14 Apr 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Serbs Launch Attack on Brcko Municipality Serbs Launch Attack on Brcko Municipality LD1404141694 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 1300 GMT 14 Apr 94 LD1404141694 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network Serbo-Croatian BFN [Text] This morning, in an attempt to widen the corridor through Bosanska Posavina, the Serbs again launched a heavy artillery and infantry attack on the free territory of Brcko municipality. Over 400 tank, howitzer, and mortar shells have landed on the Croatian village of (Bodariste). All the lines jointly held by members of the Croat Defense Council [HVO] and the Bosnia-Herzegovina Army were also pounded. Three infantry forays were attempted during these attacks, during which two HVO soldiers were killed and six wounded.
